{"consensus_set_id":"61055","translation_language":"fa","translation_source":{"hid":"409761"},"segments":[{"source_hadith_segment":"<quranic_text> « مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ رِجٰالٌ صَدَقُوا مٰا عٰاهَدُوا اللّٰهَ عَلَيْهِ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الاحزاب ۲۳ ] </footnote>  قَالَ :  « عَلِيٌّ ،  وَ حَمْزَةُ ،  وَ جَعْفَرٌ ،   <quranic_text> « فَمِنْهُمْ مَنْ قَضيٰ نَحْبَهُ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الاحزاب ۲۳ ] </footnote>   ،  قَالَ :  عَهْدَهُ ،  وَ هُوَ حَمْزَةُ ،  وَ جَعْفَرٌ  <quranic_text> « وَ مِنْهُمْ مَنْ يَنْتَظِرُ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الاحزاب ۲۳ ] </footnote>   ،  قَالَ :  عَلِيُّ بْنُ اَبِي طَالِبٍ ( عَلَيْهِ السَّلاَمُ ) » .","translation_segment":"","segment_columns":[{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مِنَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"المؤمنين","display":"الْمُؤْمِنِينَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"رجال","display":"رِجٰالٌ"},{"kind":"word","token":"صدقوا","display":"صَدَقُوا"},{"kind":"word","token":"ما","display":"مٰا"},{"kind":"word","token":"عاهدوا","display":"عٰاهَدُوا"},{"kind":"word","token":"الله","display":"اللّٰهَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"عليه","display":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الاحزاب","display":"الاحزاب"},{"kind":"word","token":"۲۳","display":"۲۳"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"قال","display":"قَالَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"علي","display":"عَلِيٌّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"حمزه","display":"حَمْزَةُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"جعفر","display":"جَعْفَرٌ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"فمنهم","display":"فَمِنْهُمْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مَنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قضي","display":"قَضيٰ"},{"kind":"word","token":"نحبه","display":"نَحْبَهُ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_ope